    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好在城市里漫游寻找隐藏的猫了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330970/extras/a1a78f81aebc934bd716892449ab8320.poster.avif?t=1729066960\" width=480 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330970/extras/a1a78f81aebc934bd716892449ab8320.webm?t=1729066960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330970/extras/a1a78f81aebc934bd716892449ab8320.mp4?t=1729066960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Zippy Detective: Cats》是一款解谜游戏，你将探索一个氛围浓厚的城市，尝试寻找隐藏的猫。游戏的目标是找到分布在城市不同部分的隐藏猫，将它们带到埃菲尔铁塔前面的区域，并赢得游戏中的所有成就。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找猫时避免飞船和等待的鹅。飞船可能会抢走你追逐的猫咪，让你难以找回它们。如果与鹅相撞，屏幕会被羽毛覆盖，你可能会输掉游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330970/extras/402f604829d193ea61902cf86774087c.poster.avif?t=1729066960\" width=480 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330970/extras/402f604829d193ea61902cf86774087c.webm?t=1729066960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330970/extras/402f604829d193ea61902cf86774087c.mp4?t=1729066960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，游戏的可定制主题为玩家提供了自由个性化体验的机会。玩家可以选择最适合自己的主题，并根据氛围环境自定义游戏体验。游戏中的四种不同主题选项为玩家提供了每次游戏时不同的氛围感受，为玩家提供了独特的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你找到骨头并把它们交给狗，它们会为你找到一只猫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330970/extras/e847c5fd517082637b8634f21d7b6b37.poster.avif?t=1729066960\" width=480 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330970/extras/e847c5fd517082637b8634f21d7b6b37.webm?t=1729066960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330970/extras/e847c5fd517082637b8634f21d7b6b37.mp4?t=1729066960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你喜欢《Hidden Folks》和《A Building Full of Cats》等解谜游戏，那么《Zippy Detective: Cats》可能是你的完美选择。快来找到城市中隐藏的猫，将它们带到埃菲尔铁塔前面的区域，并将它们送入太空吧！</p>",
